title: Readout of President Donald J. Trump’s Call with Prime Minister Justin Trudeau of Canada – The White House
content:
Statements & Releases			

		Foreign Policy	

Issued on:
May 14, 2018
President Donald J. Trump spoke today with Prime Minister Justin Trudeau of Canada to address the renegotiation of the North American Free Trade Agreement. President Trump underscored the importance of quickly concluding an agreement.
